  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"camera-lifecycle-1.0.0-beta11\" data-text=\"Camera-Lifecycle Version 1.0.0-beta11\" tabindex=\"-1\">Camera-Lifecycle Version 1.0.0-beta11</h3>\n<p>October 14, 2020</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.camera:camera-lifecycle:1.0.0-beta11</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/691e3a429902a0a3e087f28877e7cd5f668114fe..9a238add5b2df90db87d93473595ccd6911e297e/camera/camera-lifecycle\">Version 1.0.0-beta11 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">&lt;UseCase&gt;.getTargetRotation()</code> will return <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">Surface.ROTATION_0</code>\nif called before being attached to a Camera instance unless a\ntargetRotation has been set on the Builder or UseCase. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I80fcd8b33ce27e31fd3fc38b4f9b6e0a62b06bc5\">I80fcd</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
